<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉ḥwạl ạldnyạ gẖrybẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̉ḥwạl ạldnyạ gẖrybẗ .. wạlnạs fyhạ btʿạny)2
 ttḥsr ʿly̱ ywm fạt .. wtqwl lw yrjʿ tạny
 (mʿ ạ̹ny bạʿysẖ wsṭhm .. ḥạss byhm ạ̹nmạ
 msẖ bạḥzn kdh zyhm .. ʿlsẖạn ạ̉nạ wṭny ạlsmạ)
 ạlqrạr- (ʿlsẖạn ʿlsẖạn .. ʿlsẖạn ạ̉nạ wṭny ạlsmạ)2
 2- (ʿlsẖạn ạ̉nạ wṭny ạlsmạ .. mạbkẖạfsẖ mn ạlạ̉yạm)2
 ḥwạlyã qlq wʿnạ .. lkn fy ạlqlb slạm
 (wkl ywm byʿdy .. msẖ byʿjl bnhạyty
 lkn byqrb lqạ .. bạ̹lhy wsr sʿạdty)2</lyrics>
<author>nbyl wṣfy, sạmḥ rwbyl</author>
